  "header.req0title": "Base configuration — applies to all agreements",
  "header.req0detail": "In SAP IBP → Settings → Communication Management: create a Communication User, a Communication System (representing this external system) and a Communication Arrangement with the corresponding scenario. The endpoint URL is obtained from each Communication Arrangement once created.",
  "header.req1title": "SAP_COM_0326 — Application Jobs Administration",
  "header.req1detail": "Scenario \"External Scheduler — Application Job Administration Integration\". Grants full access to the BC_EXT_APPJOB_MANAGEMENT service: schedule jobs for any business user, cancel, restart and monitor jobs created by any user. Activates: Summary · Job Templates · Job Monitor.",
  "header.req2title": "SAP_COM_0068 — Integration Monitoring",
  "header.req2detail": "Scenario \"Planning: Integration Monitoring\". Exposes resource consumption (/IBP/RES_CONS_STATS_API_SRV) with CPU and memory of the tenant in % with UTC timestamps at minute level, and system task monitoring (/IBP/TASKMON_EXT_SRV) with data from the last 90 days. Activates: Resource Stats.",
  "header.req3title": "SAP_COM_0924 — Telemetry Data Integration",
  "header.req3detail": "Scenario \"Planning – Telemetry Data Integration\". Exposes the Telemetry Read API with data from the last 90 days: Excel Add-In usage (logons, planning views, key figures), Dashboards, Analytics Stories, Alert Monitor and Fiori apps by user and Planning Area. Processes personal data. Activates: Adoption · Excel Add-In · Dashboards.",
  "header.req4title": "Authentication — all agreements",
  "header.req4detail": "HTTP Basic Authentication with the Communication User and password for each agreement. Credentials are requested at sign-in and are not stored on the server.",
